[{"_id":"69a964c6c809c08797550d73","wid":"69a964c6c809c08797550d73","mag_num_id":6186374,"type":"background","color":"ffffff","opacity":1,"mute":true,"viewport_phone_portrait":{},"__v":0},{"_id":"69a964c6c809c08797550d74","wid":"69a964c6c809c08797550d74","mag_num_id":6186374,"type":"text","x":168,"y":101,"w":265,"h":2215,"version":3,"verticalAlign":"top","textDirection":"LTR","autosize":false,"blocks":[{"key":"abbn7","text":"IMPRINT\n\n\nResponsible for this website\nDott. Massimiliano Marian, trading as:\n\nRiviera Moretti\nArchitectural Visualisation \n\nMoretti Rapid\nDesign Support, Art Direction & Graphic Communication (on-site or remote)\n\n\n\nKettenbrückengasse 17/21\n1050 Vienna, Austria\n\nEmail: office@riviera-moretti.com\n\nVAT ID: ATU67702738\nIBAN: AT52 1200 0529 3502 7805\n\nAll images and content © Riviera Moretti 2026, unless otherwise credited.\nAll rights reserved.\n\n\nThis legal notice is provided in English. In case of doubt or dispute, \nthe English version shall prevail.\n\n\n\n\n\nDISCLAIMER\n\n\nAll content on this website has been created with the greatest possible care. Nevertheless, no guarantee is provided for completeness, accuracy, or timeliness.\nRiviera Moretti accepts no responsibility for the content of external websites. The responsibility for linked content lies solely with the respective providers. If any legal infringements become known, such links will be removed immediately.\n\n\n\n\n\nPRIVACY POLICY\n\n\nRiviera Moretti is committed to protecting your personal data and complies with the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).\nThis policy explains how your data is collected, processed, stored, and protected when you visit this website or contact Riviera Moretti.\n\n\n\n\n\nDATA COLLECTED\n\n\nContact Data:\nWhen you contact Riviera Moretti (via email or otherwise), the personal data you provide (e.g., name, email address, and any other information you include) is used exclusively to process your request. Data will be deleted as soon as it is no longer required, unless legal retention obligations apply.\n\nAnalytics Data:\nThis website uses Google Analytics (Google Ireland Limited) to analyse traffic and improve performance. The following anonymised data may be collected:\n - IP address\n - Browser type and version\n - Operating system\n - Referrer URL\n - Date and time of access\n - Pages visited\n\nThis helps Riviera Moretti understand how the site is used and improve the user experience. You may disable tracking via browser settings or Google’s opt-out tools.\n\nHosting:\nThe website is created and delivered using Readymag (Readymag Inc., USA). Content is hosted on Readymag’s infrastructure, which may apply its own cookie and analytics tools. For more information, please refer to Readymag’s Privacy Policy.\n\n\n\n\n\nLEGAL BASIS FOR PROCESSING\n\n\nThe legal basis for processing personal data is:\n - Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR – Consent (e.g., when you contact Riviera Moretti)\n - Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR – Legitimate interest (e.g., in website optimisation and analytics)\n\n\n\n\n\nDATA RETENTION\n\n\nPersonal data is retained only as long as necessary for its purpose or to meet legal obligations. Regular reviews are carried out to ensure data is deleted when no longer required.\n\n\n\n\n\nDATA SHARING\n\n\nRiviera Moretti does not sell, share, or transfer personal data to third parties, except where legally required or with explicit consent.\n\n\n\n\n\nYOUR RIGHTS\n\n\nUnder GDPR, you have the right to:\n - Access your personal data\n - Request correction or deletion\n - Restrict or object to processing\n - Request data portability (in a structured, machine-readable format)\n - Lodge a complaint with the Austrian Data Protection Authority (Datenschutzbehörde)\n\nTo exercise these rights, please contact:\noffice@riviera-moretti.com\n\n\n\n\n\nCOOKIES\n\n\nThis site is hosted via Readymag, which provides a cookie banner for managing user consent. Riviera Moretti does not set additional cookies beyond those necessary for functionality and Google Analytics.\n\n\n\n\n\nCONTACT\n\n\nFor privacy-related inquiries, please contact:\noffice@riviera-moretti.com\n\n\n\n\n\nLEGACY NOTE\n\n\nThis website serves as a digital archive of projects and visualisations created by Riviera Moretti in collaboration with architectural studios. All architectural designs remain the intellectual property of the respective studios.\n\nRiviera Moretti’s role is limited to architectural visualisations, while Moretti Rapid provided in-house support for design development, visual communication, and related services, depending on project needs.\n\nAll projects are credited accordingly. The intention is solely to document Riviera Moretti’s contribution as a freelance partner—not to claim authorship or ownership of the designs.\nAll work was conducted independently under freelance contracts, without employment or subordinate relationships with commissioning studios. Contributions were always developed within the framework of external consultancy and creative partnership.\n\n\n\n\n\nIMAGE RIGHTS & USAGE TERMS\n\n\nUnless otherwise agreed in writing, Riviera Moretti reserves the right to publish visual material produced for competitions, presentations, or design proposals after official jury announcements or once projects are publicly confirmed by the commissioning party.\nSuch use is strictly limited to Riviera Moretti’s own portfolio, website, or professional presentations.\n\nIf confidentiality is required, this must be explicitly stated at the beginning of the project. Riviera Moretti will fully respect such agreements when clearly defined in advance.\nAll images remain the intellectual property of Riviera Moretti unless transferred by contract.\n\nArchitectural studios may publish images created by Riviera Moretti on their websites or social media, provided that clear credit is given.\n\nAny further commercial use—such as real estate marketing, advertising campaigns, or publications—requires prior written consent.\n\nIn cases of unauthorised use, especially where confidentiality requirements were not disclosed at the project’s outset, Riviera Moretti reserves the right to take appropriate measures to protect authorship and usage rights.\n\n\n\n\n\nLAST UPDATE: FEBRUARY 2026\n\n\nPlease note that the contents of this legal notice, including the imprint, privacy policy, usage terms, and image rights, may be updated or revised from time to time to reflect legal requirements or changes in service scope. Users are kindly advised to review this page periodically to stay informed about the current terms.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWe thank you sincerely for your time and interest in our work.\n\n\nWith Love,\nRiviera  Moretti\n\n\n\n\n\n","entityRanges":[{"offset":3572,"length":26,"key":0}],"depth":0}],"styles":[{"key":"abbn7","type":"unstyled","inlineStyles":{"styles":[{"offset":0,"length":8,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":559,"length":13,"styles":["0;0"]},{"offset":979,"length":15,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":1269,"length":15,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":2312,"length":28,"styles":["0;0","5;15"]},{"offset":2556,"length":16,"styles":["0;0","5;15"]},{"offset":2759,"length":14,"styles":["0;0","5;15"]},{"offset":2917,"length":12,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":3297,"length":8,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":3515,"length":8,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":3604,"length":12,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":4493,"length":27,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":5666,"length":27,"styles":["0;0","1;1","5;15"]},{"offset":6105,"length":16,"styles":["0;0","5;10","8;13"]},{"offset":559,"length":11,"styles":["1;1"]},{"offset":2312,"length":27,"styles":["1;1"]},{"offset":2556,"length":15,"styles":["1;1"]},{"offset":2759,"length":13,"styles":["1;1"]},{"offset":8,"length":2,"styles":["1;2"]},{"offset":553,"length":6,"styles":["1;2"]},{"offset":570,"length":2,"styles":["1;2"]},{"offset":973,"length":6,"styl